OL,3,CBurst water main affecting areas of
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,FBottled water stations have been
OL,7,Fopened as a burst water main is
OL,8,Faffecting areas of Cardiff.
OL,10,FTeams from Dwr Cymru Welsh Water have
OL,11,Fbeen working through Wednesday night
OL,12,Fto attempt to fix the issue affecting
OL,13,Fthe Llanrumney and St Mellons areas of
OL,14,Fthe city.
OL,16,FIt is hoped supplies will return by
OL,17,Fthis afternoon.
OL,19,FBottled water stations are available
