OL,3,CBurst water main affecting areas of
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,FIn a statement, the company said:
OL,7,F"We're aware of a burst on our network
OL,8,Fwhich is affecting the water supply to
OL,9,Fthis area. Until the pipe is fixed,
OL,10,Fyou may experience low pressure and
OL,11,Fdiscolouration to your water supply,
OL,12,For no water.
OL,14,F"We have a team working to restore
OL,15,Fsupplies by this afternoon. We
OL,16,Fapologise for any inconvenience
OL,17,Fcaused."
